#######Interaction Parameters##########

#########Set up system#################
fix	1 all nve
fix	2 all langevin 1.0 1.0 1.0 188801
########################################

compute Rg_compute polymer gyration
compute myPE all pe

#######Run simulation###########################
thermo_style    custom step temp etotal ke pe epair ebond evdwl ecoul c_Rg_compute c_myPE
timestep	0.005
neigh_modify delay 0 every 1 check yes